      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@\n+created: 2025-12-28\n+title: Pull Request Workflow\n+intro: >-\n+  This release adds the new `/git:pr` command for creating GitHub pull requests directly\n+  from Claude Code. The command integrates with `/git:commit` to streamline the workflow\n+  from staging changes to opening a PR. Additionally, `/git:commit` has been simplified\n+  by removing changelog and version bump steps, which are now handled separately via\n+  `/changelog:add` and `/changelog:release`."
