      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+This release introduces the `tql:writing-programs` skill, which provides TQL language fundamentals and spawns the `docs:reader` subagent for live documentation lookup. This helps guide you through writing correct TQL programs by providing language foundations upfront and on-demand reference material.\n+\n+## \ud83d\ude80 Features\n+\n+### TQL program authoring skill with documentation lookup\n+\n+The `tql:writing-programs` skill loads TQL language fundamentals and spawns the `docs:reader` subagent for live documentation lookup. This guides you through writing correct TQL programs by providing language foundations upfront and on-demand reference material.\n+\n+*By @mavam and @claude.*"
